This is a python generated website which display my favorite movies and shows a triler for each movie. To view the trailer for each movie, follow these instructions to install.

WINDOWS

1. Make sure you have python installed in your PC. To get python, visit https://www.python.org

2. Download or fork from https://github.com/edwinaquino/movietrailers.

3. Unzip the files.

4. Open entertainment_center.py by right-clicking and selecting Open or Double click to start the application.

5. To view a movie trailer, click on the movie image to view the trailer. ENJOY!


